    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic ride. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who needs a dependable daily driver that still looks great on the road. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and it drives smoothly! If you\u2019re looking for a well-loved vehicle that's ready for many more adventures, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
