    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six. This high-revving power plant delivers linear throttle response via individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Performance is anchored by a factory limited-slip differential and a chassis that has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement. The VANOS system has been serviced, and rod bearings were addressed recently, ensuring the internal kinetics remain within spec. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with its driver-grade status, the suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings. A purist-spec example ready for the apex.",
